data.description:
Now weather will always make you smile.
Be pleasantly surprised by the new screen color every time weather was updated.

Always will notify you when bluetooth connection lost by vibration (except cases when watch is plugged to charge or DoNotDisturb mode turned on).
Battery status will always be shown on low charge.

- A lot of colors for screen background that updates randomly or set static color in the settings;
- Current weather of your location or any custom location you entered in the settings;
- Temperature in Fahrenheit or Celsius as you decide;
- Two weather servers: YahooWeather and OpenWeatherMap;
- Time in 12h or 24h format based on your watch's preference;
- Current date and day of week;
- Humidity;
- Hourly vibration;
- Do not disturb mode.

You can also setup to show always bluetooth status and battery charge if you want.

Just try. You'll like it!

Finally, a lightweight COLOR version of Pebble's original Big Time watchface! Pebble's easiest-to-read digital face, with selectable color and these new configurable features:
1. Ability to set each digit to a different color (red/green for Christmas, blue/white for Hanukkah, purple/gold/white/orange for Festivus);
2. An optional analog second hand (we know how useful they can be);
3. An optional date and two-week calendar, which appears upon wrist shake (duration is configurable);
4. An optional battery indicator; and
5. An optional Bluetooth-connection icon to alert you if your watch has disconnected from your phone (yes, it'll vibrate on disconnect/reconnect).

Also, for a short time only and for no adequately-explored reason other than it's winter here in the Northern Hemisphere, optional snow-covered digits (no impact on battery life)!

